dc_description_s: This data layer represents zoning for Sauk County, Wisconsin in 2014. [This feature class is used to maintain and display the current zoning information in the Sauk County GIS. Zoning Districts are administered by Sauk County for all Towns except the Town of Fairfield, Town of Delton, Town of Merrimac, and the Town of Washington.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://data-saukgis.opendata.arcgis.com.
